<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc., bekennen
                                <expan>offenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mit disem
                            <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> umb sölich
                            anderhalb<expan>hund<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>new<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ung<ex>er</ex>isch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>jerlich<ex>er</ex></expan> gült, die wir von dem
                                <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vest<ex>en</ex></expan> ritter <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und
                        frawn <expan>Elspet<ex>en</ex></expan> Marschelkin von Pappenheim, seinr
                                <expan>elich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n,</ex></expan> ausz dem sloss, veste und stat Hilpoltstein
                        mit <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>zugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> umb drewtawsent
                            <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>new<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ungrisch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> kawfft <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nach
                        lawt und sag des hawbtbriefs, den wir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz uns die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und
                        fraw Elspet, sein eliche <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, zweyrtawsent
                                <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>new<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ungris<ex>cher</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> daran <expan>v<ex>er</ex>weiset</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> lieben
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Weigel
                            <expan>Gras<ex>er</ex></expan>, der auch uns umb
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zweytawsent
                            <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> ein gut <expan>genüg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        getan hat. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>sag<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir die <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Ros<ex>enberg</ex></expan> und
                        frawn <expan>Elspet<ex>en,</ex></expan> sein eliche
                            <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, und ir <expan>erb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        der <expan>egeschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> zweyrtawsent
                            <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> newr <expan>ungrisch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> für uns und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>nachkom<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> quitt, ledig und lose mit disem
                                <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> doch unschedlich uns und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nach <expan>kom<ex>en</ex></expan> an
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>brief<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>bürg<ex>en</ex></expan> umb die
                                <expan>übrig<ex>en</ex></expan> tawsent gut new ungrisch
                                <expan>guld<ex>en,</ex></expan> bis wir der auch beczalt
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
                        dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> zu ruck
                                <expan>aufgedruckte<ex>n</ex></expan> insigel.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
